{"tid":2006634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明個運動點解淡........","createTime":"2020-05-08T02:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T03:05:11.000Z","uid":202496,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fecb0918098660b1b1592b4e537b54bacc5b3f","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"其實運動開始淡嘅係因為你哋<span style=\"color: red;\">自己</span><br />\n<br />\n試想當初 一個行動前一晚嘅文宣同宣傳 甚至係啲group入面都好 有家會講嘅係<span style=\"color: purple;\">聽日見！</span> <span style=\"color: violet;\">不見不散</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家呢？每一個行動都只係有人質疑 有人埋怨行動內容 就算係鬼搞出嚟嘅活動 我地個個肯出反而要多謝佢比機會我地聚人添<br />\n<br />\n仲有嘅係有人用幽默(懶係)嘅言氣 好似係<span style=\"color: red;\">要返工 不了</span> 自問你睇到嘅會係有咩感受？質疑活動成效？返工重要啲？之後呢種心態就會一傳十 十傳百 最後係點就自己知<br />\n<br />\n同埋香港人嘅舌頭太過勁 一句唔岩 意見唔合就開始鬧交 香港人鬧交勁呢樣文化可唔可以唔好對自己人用 你係網絡同佢鬧交 但佢可能係曾經救過你 係企係你隔離嘅手足一齊打緊仗 散果陣仲有講有笑<br />\n<br />\n所以要改善嘅係咩？係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">心態同語氣</span></span>呀 爭氣啦香港人 我哋俾人踩到上心口啦 狗都笑我地啦 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">可以比意見但唔可以譴責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[black]<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復完香港我講大家食buffet</span>[/black]</span>"},{"pid":"a0e8691fcd622155b0a1611a1184b06b3b0497ec","tid":2006634,"uid":103914,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"要食m記 不了"},{"pid":"5ee39e18bc2655434a69b203fe961e2dff8ab5c4","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"隱藏訊息已暴露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b454aecdf05f11fbda22c95a6eae9819103879c8","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"dd67f2f5e04f84f7b0d0bd35b5ac67369ddc8da7","tid":2006634,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"每一個行動都只係有人質疑<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過係有五毛帶風向"},{"pid":"dbef8137a6d150704cee0e9b4988103d8e3a65ff","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"fc769d201c2e09aefa88ebb1137740b176a7e358","tid":2006634,"uid":321090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"我要你請<br />\n唔要你講"},{"pid":"d1cdf80c51a889517509dca3c903712ba2ceca04","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd67f2f5e04f84f7b0d0bd35b5ac67369ddc8da7","tid":2006634,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"每一個行動都只係有人質疑<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過係有五毛帶風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"我見到自己識嘅人都變到係咁 五毛固然有 不過唔應該比佢哋咁輕易帶風向 我估香港人冇咁蠢"},{"pid":"376d8d912cd384fc10c1d9b551634c360b82160b","tid":2006634,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08QVX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08QVX2.jpg&h=57e88f23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxzXAX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxzXAX2.jpg&h=fe0bfceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrkzDbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrkzDbo.jpg&h=e0310cb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4c79e5e1e472c1316e57127eea17478f064179a","tid":2006634,"uid":202496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc769d201c2e09aefa88ebb1137740b176a7e358","tid":2006634,"uid":321090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"我要你請<br />\n唔要你講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"請請請請請請請請請請 罰抄10次"},{"pid":"8adf0295c7a61b2a713091ded7327e03965607c0","tid":2006634,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd67f2f5e04f84f7b0d0bd35b5ac67369ddc8da7","tid":2